ring Boot Kafka, Spring Integration Kafka, and Kafka client dependencies transitively, and its own public surface includes configuration/property, header-mapping, topic utility, and provisioning classes that can be exercised without adding a broker, optional starter, or test dependency.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"No required environment variables or system properties. Meaningful tests should focus on the core artifact surface that does not require a live Kafka broker, such as Kafka binder configuration properties, Spring Boot property binding, BinderHeaderMapper, KafkaTopicUtils/BindingUtils behavior, and provisioner error-path behavior with unreachable or stubbed admin settings.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Full end-to-end Spring Cloud Stream Kafka binding with real produce/consume traffic normally requires a Kafka broker, but that is not necessary before meaningful coverage of the requested core artifact is reachable.\",\n    \"The documented application dependency for normal users is spring-cloud-stream-binder-kafka or spring-cloud-starter-stream-kafka, while this issue targets the lower-level spring-cloud-stream-binder-kafka-core artifact; adding the non-core binder would shift coverage away from the requested artifact.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b6483e97d07d161016a41a40d432881979265ee8f3b0a4a31\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 3603, "output": 783, "cacheRead": 45568, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 49954, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782686721461, "responseId": "resp_0b6483e97d07d161016a41a40236ac8197a386861af32fe2a0"}}
